data.description: Don't Miss this Beautiful home that was just completely remodeled and ready to move into. This 2 bed house will surprise you once you enter with the spacious rooms, beautiful Kitchen featuring quartz counters and beautiful appliances. Current furniture in home is also negotiable. Enjoy entertaining in the huge fenced yard with mature trees. Large attached carport to protect your cars from storms. Located off the beaten path away from town but still close enough to get to all your shopping and the highway. Come check this home which is priced less than many mobile homes selling in area.
